Week 4

- Cloud security concern
- data loss and leakage
- insecure interfaces and APIs
- Identify access management - first line of defence
- apps on cloud can authenticate users, cloud directory, google, twitter
- sometimes API keys - can identify user
- multi factor autentication, single user PINS, tokens, change in location
- securely manage user profiles
- directory service in cloud
- reporting - user centric view
- which users have access to which resource
- under which conditions
- provisioning users by specifyinhg roles for each user
- password length, one time password
- deprovising of access once people leave
- access group, target, service offerings
- role - actions allowed
- access groups, streamline access assignment
